sql:
SELECT title
   FROM demographic_reports
   WHERE report_status = 'draft';

external_knowledge:
Eldest refers to the highest age; 
married daughters refers to the individuals with a relation type of 'Daughter' and a marital status of 'Married'; 
most children refers to the highest number of children among their siblings.

- 'Top 10 earners' refers to those with the highest income within their respective racial and sex groups, as ranked by the query; 
- 'Insured' means having health insurance; 
- 'Full-time' refers to the employment status of an individual; 
- 'Married or single' refers to the marital status of an individual.
